Package: heatmapHIV
Title: Produce heatmaps for RNA-Seq HIV data
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Joly Beauparlant", role=c("aut", "cre"),
    email="Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca")
Description: This package is a wrapper aroung the heatmaps.2 function from
    the gplots package to make is as easy as possible to produce an heatmap.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
BiocViews: RNA-Seq, MultipleComparison, Genetics
Imports: gplots
Suggests: knitr, testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
